<div id="pf4ecd" class="pf w58 h34f" data-page-no="4ecd"><div class="pc pc4ecd w58 h34f"><div class="t m139 x4e h28 y3024 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m791 x83 h28 y2fb2 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Levitical order had a line of priests but the new order has </div><div class="t m5 x55 h28 y2e61 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m1abf x79 h28 y2e61 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only </div><div class="t m5 x45 h28 y2e61 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m6bc x62 h28 y2dac ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">priest (verses 23, 24). </div><div class="t m13e x60 h28 y2a18 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m45e x83 h28 y29dd ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Under the new order Christ continues </div><div class="t m5 xac h28 y29dc ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m7f1 xc7 h28 y29ac ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(verse 24). </div><div class="t m142 x60 h28 y2a67 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m8a x83 h28 y2a6d ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Under this order Christ is able to </div><div class="t m5 x4b h28 y2a6d ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m13e4 xca h28 y2c05 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(verse 25). </div><div class="t m145 x60 h28 y2331 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m311 x83 h28 y242b ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As priest of the new order Christ is </div><div class="t m5 x9 h28 y2424 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m7f1 xc7 h28 y28b6 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(verse 26). </div><div class="t m148 x60 h28 y1f10 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m162c x83 h28 y1f10 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ has no need to offer </div><div class="t m5 xaf h28 y1f10 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m7f1 xc7 h28 y20ba ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(verse 27). </div><div class="t m14b x60 h28 y1278 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m167 x83 h28 y14e6 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mortals served as priests under the Levitical system but Christ is </div><div class="t m55e x83 h28 y9eb ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">consecrated </div><div class="t m5 x82 h28 y9eb ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t me44 xc7 h28 y1038 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(verse 28). </div><div class="t m1d7f x74 h28 y14d4 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY AND MEDITATION: </div><div class="t md0d x60 h28 y1230 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read </div><div class="t m1067 x12 h2c y1230 ff6 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Early Writings, </div><div class="t m1ad2 x89 h28 y9ee ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pages 250-256. </div><div class="t mb42 x4e h28 y97c ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The record tells us nothing about his [Melchizedek&apos;s] pedigree, his </div><div class="t mf42 x74 h28 y4de ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">birth, or death. So far as the record goes, no beginning nor end of life is </div><div class="t me73 x74 h28 yd1c ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">given; and it was the custom, therefore, among the Jews, to speak of such </div><div class="t m93f x74 h28 yd03 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as having no genealogy, no mother, no father, no beginning of days, nor </div><div class="t m112a x74 h28 ydb1 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">end of life. And considering that all these expressions are used simply </div><div class="t md32 x74 h28 ya11 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">from the standpoint of the record, there is no difficulty. Melchizedek sud-</div><div class="t m314 x74 h28 yad5 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">denly appears upon the scene of action, an eminent servant of God, com-</div><div class="t m688 x74 h28 yad6 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bining, in his own person the double office of king and priest. All before </div><div class="t m191a x74 h28 y76c ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">him is blank; all following him is blank. Neither birth nor death appearing </div><div class="t m28d x74 h28 y113e ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in the scene, he becomes a fitting prototype of Christ in his position of </div><div class="t mddc x74 h28 yf31 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">priest-king in this dispensation.&quot;—Uriah Smith, </div><div class="t m34c x8a h2c ya92 ff6 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Review and Herald, </div><div class="t m35e x74 h28 ydb5 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Nov. 5, 1895. </div><div class="t m149f x74 h28 y7d8 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: The knowledge that we have a merciful, compassionate High </div><div class="t m517 x74 h28 y15fb ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Priest in heaven gives us strong confidence. He is the one and only true </div><div class="t m3f0 x74 h28 y11af ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Priest; His priesthood is superior to every other priesthood, the Levitical </div><div class="t m256 x74 h28 yf0a ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">order included. We need no other mediator, no human priest. </div><div class="t m5bc x73 h28 y7dd ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">APPLICATION: </div><div class="t m1c2 x74 h28 y897 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">o </div><div class="t m775 x4e h28 y11f5 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What difference does it make to me to know that I have &quot;such an high </div><div class="t m454 x4e h28 ycf0 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">priest&quot;? Consider, for example, does it make a difference: when I feel </div><div class="t m1178 x4e h28 y1361 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">discouraged? in my concept of heaven? in my hour of test? </div><div class="t m1c2 x74 h28 y938 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">o </div><div class="t mcdd x4e h28 yfc2 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sometimes we feel lonely and wonder if anyone cares. Do the ideas </div><div class="t me46 x4e h28 y7e2 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">presented in this lesson suggest where I can find help? </div><div class="t m1c2 x74 h28 yf81 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">o </div><div class="t m55d x4e h28 y968 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How can I make the marvelous truths of this lesson real to others? </div><div class="t m13b1 x74 h28 y1364 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTES: </div><div class="t m134d x73 h1 y21b2 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">62 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
